    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! Up for grabs today is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed on Sundays, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape; the paint has a mirror finish and the interior still has that fresh, clean feel that\u2019s so hard to find. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but honestly, she looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019m only letting her go to a good home where she'll be appreciated. Come on by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I'm so head-over-heels for this one!",
